name: adidas trx vintage
description: The adidas TRX Vintage is a retro-inspired sneaker with a classic look and modern comfort. It features a suede and nylon upper, a cushioned insole, and a durable rubber outsole for traction and support.

name: nike dunk high retro
description: The Nike Dunk High Retro is a stylish and versatile shoe with a classic design. It features a leather upper for durability and support, and a rubber outsole for traction on a variety of surfaces.

name: air jordan 7 retro q
description: The Air Jordan 7 Retro Q is a classic basketball shoe with a sleek design and superior performance. It features a leather and synthetic upper, a full-length Air-Sole unit for cushioning, and a rubber outsole for traction.

name: adidas adizero adios pro 3.0
description: The adidas adizero adios pro 3.0 is a high-performance running shoe designed for speed and efficiency. It features a lightweight construction, responsive cushioning, and a carbon fiber plate for added support and stability.

name: puma x ray2 square SD
description: Puma X-Ray2 Square SD: A casual sneaker with a chunky silhouette and a retro-inspired design, featuring a durable leather and mesh upper and a comfortable SoftFoam+ insole for all-day cushioning. The shoe also features Puma branding and a square toe design.

name: jordan vachetta tan
description: The Jordan Vachetta Tan is a premium sneaker with a stylish and sleek design. It features a leather upper with perforations for breathability, and a rubber outsole for durability and traction.

name: adidas forum mid parley
description: The adidas Forum Mid Parley is a stylish and eco-friendly sneaker made from recycled ocean plastic. It features a classic design with modern materials, including a breathable mesh upper and a comfortable EVA midsole.

name: jordan zoom separate
description: The Jordan Zoom Separate is a high-performance basketball shoe designed for speed and agility on the court. It features a lightweight and breathable upper, responsive Zoom Air cushioning, and a durable rubber outsole.

name: nike dunk high 1985
description: The Nike Dunk High 1985 is a retro basketball shoe with a classic design. It features a leather and synthetic upper for durability and support, and a rubber outsole for traction on the court.

name: jordan series mid
description: The Jordan Series Mid is a stylish and comfortable shoe with the iconic Jumpman logo on the side. It features a leather and synthetic upper for durability and support, while the Air-Sole unit in the heel provides cushioning.

name: nike lebron 9 low
description: The Nike LeBron 9 Low is a high-performance basketball shoe designed for LeBron James' signature style of play. It features a Flywire-infused upper for lightweight support and a Max Air unit in the heel for cushioning.

name: nike pegasus turbo next nature
description: The Nike Pegasus Turbo Next Nature is a high-performance running shoe with a sleek and stylish design. It features a lightweight and breathable upper, responsive ZoomX foam cushioning, and a durable rubber outsole.

name: puma softride enzo NXT
description: Puma Softride Enzo NXT: A versatile training shoe with a softfoam midsole and a breathable mesh upper for maximum comfort and support during any workout. The shoe also features Puma branding and a stylish design.

name: nike sb dunk high pro
description: Nike SB Dunk High Pro: A high-top sneaker with a classic design, featuring a durable leather upper and a rubber outsole for excellent grip and traction. The Nike SB Dunk High Pro is a favorite among skateboarders and sneaker enthusiasts alike.

name: nike zoom freak 4
description: Nike Zoom Freak 4: A basketball shoe designed for Milwaukee Bucks superstar Giannis Antetokounmpo, featuring a responsive Zoom Air unit and a durable rubber outsole for excellent traction on the court. The shoe also features a unique design inspired by Giannis' Greek heritage.

name: puma anzarun lite bold
description: Puma Anzarun Lite Bold: A lightweight running shoe with a breathable mesh upper and a cushioned midsole for all-day comfort. The shoe also features bold Puma branding and a sleek, modern design.
